{"tid":516028,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「核按鈕在我桌上」 金正恩元旦宣佈︰專注核彈頭作戰部署","createTime":"2018-01-01T03:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T16:49:27.000Z","uid":20933,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"aed684522ecf068a16c900c8d8b8733f6883d513","tid":516028,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:29:50.000Z","msg":"北韓領袖金正恩周一宣佈，北韓已發展有能力攻擊美國本土的核武器，而美國永遠都不能展開對付北韓的戰爭，平壤將專注核彈頭的作戰部署。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩周一透過電視發表元旦致辭「示威」，他表示，「整個美國都在我們的核武器射程內，而核按鈕一直在我桌上，這是事實，不是威脅」，一旦北韓安全受到威脅時，就會使用核武器。他又表示，北韓將專注進行核彈頭以及彈道導彈的作戰部署。<br />\n<br />\n另外，金正恩對南韓釋出善意，指兩韓關係應該改善，「對話的大門已經開啟」，他又祝賀平昌冬奧成功舉辦，又指會考慮派代表參加冬奧。"},{"pid":"c4e764568d19e20609b222fc6016ee8c31bfd2df","tid":516028,"uid":6959,"like":50,"dislike":5,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:32:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f52a35b9f4be8cafad7d9a0f8cdd68e0fb3a2d5a","tid":516028,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cf623e4f076135598fd99b7d49d60ccca8381a","tid":516028,"uid":63845,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"迎接未來既對話"},{"pid":"c6663ecce69d139337d3be2b4643ff199e4feb6a","tid":516028,"uid":8867,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:37:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7872152d991fb2b074189491d532a28be77399f8","tid":516028,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:38:16.000Z","msg":"正恩真係幾型"},{"pid":"a16c20b58352adfa91d46b684b62c0010c9f5af3","tid":516028,"uid":53794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4e764568d19e20609b222fc6016ee8c31bfd2df","tid":516028,"uid":6959,"like":50,"dislike":5,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:32:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"thanks obama"},{"pid":"50421b60faeed08b2aabf140cd34acdee220bb8c","tid":516028,"